summary: TAKATA RECALL  I WAS DRIVING STRAIGHT ABOUT 50MPH ON A CITY STREET AND MY BACK WINDSHIELD EXPLODED. MY REAR DEFROST WAS ON.THE HOLES WERE DIRECTLY WHERE THE DEFROST CORDS WERE. THE CORDS WERE STICKING OUT AND THE GLASS WAS GONE ON THOSE TWO SPOTS. THE DEFROST CORD TIPS ARE BLACK AS IF THEY WERE BURNT. I CALLED THE POLICE AND THEY NOTICED MY WINDSHIELD WAS PUSHED OUT AND NOT IN, SO NOTHING COULD HAVE HIT MY CAR.
